data.description: Charming Turn Of The Century Farmhouse W/4 Beds & 3 Baths Sitting On Just Under 1 Acre. It Boasts An Inviting Front Porch & Foyer, Some Original Hardwood Floors & Wood Slats On The Wall & Ceilings.the Formal Dining Room Could Also Be Used For A Bedroom Or Office. The Updated Kitchen W/a Dining Area Holds A Large Table, As Well As, A Pantry. The Sunroom Allows Extra Light Into The Kitchen. The Living Room Has A Gas Fireplace. There Are Two Full Bathrooms On The Main Level. Upstairs You Will Find 2 Bedrooms & The Primary Bedroom W/ensuite. Outside There Is An Attached Carport, 2 Car Detached Garage & One Car Detached Garage W/workshop. Lots Of Space Outside To Entertain. Sellers Are Offering A 14 Month Home Warranty.
